NK041(di)032:1: mdos zor sha khrag gtor ma 'dis //
NK041(di)032:2: da lta rnal 'byor bdag bcag la //
NK041(di)032:3: sde brgyad chad pa byung ba zlog /
NK041(di)032:4: byad zor phur kha thams cad zlog /
NK041(di)032:5: lha 'dre'i za kha zug pa rgyal po lo yi
NK041(di)032:6: bdun zur blon po zla ba'i dbang btsan dmag mi
NK041(di)032:7: zhag gi dpung grangs mtshon cha bdud kyi rno ngar
NK041(di)032:8: spar kha'i skya mda' zug pa sme ba dur du
NK041(di)032:9: tshud pa sa bdag ko long gdug rtsub 'byung ba'i
NK041(di)032:10: dgra gshed 'thab pa gza' skar dus tshod ngan pa
NK041(di)032:11: lo zla zhag dus bab pa khrom dang byad du
NK041(di)032:12: bcug pa hom dang par bu bskor ba dgra chen
NK041(di)032:13: bdud du long ba ltas ngan glo bur ye 'drogs
NK041(di)032:14: dus min 'chi ba rnam brgyad mi kha bra mchu
NK041(di)032:15: thams cad chag che nyam nga thams cad sngon sgugs
NK041(di)032:16: phyi nas ded pa dgra sna phung sna gyod sna
NK041(di)032:17: nad sna yams sna rigs sna dgra sri rmi ngan
NK041(di)032:18: thams cad che sri chung sri rgas sri gzhon sri
NK041(di)032:19: dar sri god sri dgra sri mtshon sri nad sri
NK041(di)032:20: mdor na srid pa'i chag sgo dang //
NK041(di)032:21: bdag la gnod pa'i dgra bgegs rnams //
NK041(di)032:22: sdang byed dgra yi steng du zlog /
NK041(di)032:23: gnod byed bgegs kyi steng du bar chad bdud kyi steng du za 'dre phung 'dre'i steng du zlog /
